description: Try our easy to follow Beef & Bean Enchiladas recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Beef & Bean Enchiladas Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Fill wraps with mince mixture, roll up and place into a 1.5L baking dish. Sprinkle with cheese and bake for 20 minutes or until cheese is melted and starting to turn golden. Top enchiladas with lettuce, tomato and coriander to serve.
